Migration
People are migrating from one country to another. They are also bringing their culture and religion with them, fostering a more diverse society.

Food
Unilever has brought ice cream to markets, with the double-heart logo under 26 names. They sell a large amount of ice cream globally. Go to Australia or New Zealand to get a ice cream cowboy with bubble-gum for a nose, or Greece for Chocolate Orgy flavour Scandal.
